{"type": "article", "id": 35790, "title": "Bobbi Brown离职，以及，乐高明年四月在日本开园 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-20T02:50:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 929, "name": "乐高"}, {"id": 1311, "name": "变形金刚"}, {"id": 16038, "name": "BAPE"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 9254, "name": "Bobbi Brown"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161220102522pta2F1dQOqM7Rkrs.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/tom-ford-reportedly-looking-to-diversify-into-underwear-and-watches/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tom Ford 要新增男士内衣和手表线</b></a> | 有消息称，目前 Tom Ford 正在与某个男装内衣厂商进行洽谈。至于手表线方面，据称 Tom Ford 可能会进入 1500-2500 美元这个价位的手表市场。不过，目前的消息针对这两个新的举措还未出现更为具体的报道。</p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://luxe.co/post/51862/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2017/2018 秋冬巴黎男装周发布官方日程，两位中国设计师入选 </a></b>| 2017/2018 秋冬巴黎男装周将于 2017年 1 月 18-22日举行，中国独立设计师品牌孙小峰 Sean Suen，以及上官喆 SANKUANZ  入选。这次时装周上，Lucien Pellat Finet 仍是时装周开幕品牌，Kenzo 则是闭幕品牌。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/color-cosmetics/makeup-artist-bobbi-brown-ending-a-chapter-10730959/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美妆大师 Bobbi Brown 将在年末会离开自己创造的品牌</b></a> | Bobbi Brown 的母公司雅诗兰黛在周一宣布，该品牌的创始人 Bobbi Brown 将结束她 25 年的职业生涯，在年末离开公司。品牌的全球总裁 Peter Lichtenthal，将继续监管业务。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>日本首座乐高乐园将于明年 4 月 1 日正式开幕。这个乐园位于日本名古屋，将有 7 个不同的主题区，超过 40 个游乐设施及景点，同时展出超过一万只乐高模型。<a href=\"https://www.legoland.jp/en/tickets/buy-tickets/\" rel=\"nofollow\">票价</a>为成人 6900 日元，儿童 5300 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101611jAwCPqkYF4JcB72a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101611q7uWbe4T01UHMYsf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667804\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>设计师清水庆三为日本时尚名店 Nepenthes 的自家品牌 Needles，打造了 2017 春夏全新<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/needles-2017-ss-asymmetric-ghillie-sneaker\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Asymmetric Ghillie Sneaker 系列</a>。该系列共有灰白、黑色和酒红色三色，将帆布鞋面和绒面材料结合，同时加入硫化处理，呈现出特别的复古感。这款鞋可于 <a href=\"http://nepenthes.shop-pro.jp/?mode=srh&amp;sort=n&amp;keyword=ASYMMETRIC+GHILLIE+SNEAKER\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nepenthes</a> 网店购买，售价为 27000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612201016314LmshHXcAdbn3CT8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101644AI7otQvscyFDfS1z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101644flLciF3r1ykAWuC8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101652cLwlGUBiskCfAVzd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101652jnDxrH7eLMNvJcGp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101652foWcC1mP5wUgQzIR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101652I49qkhOgBLVUXeAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>觉得 Vetements 与 Reebok 的联名鞋款太难买的话，可以考虑入手双方的联名袜款。目前，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/18/vetements-reebok-socks/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements 和 Reebok 携手推出了四款联名袜子</a>，并加入了 Vetements 最具代表性的标语 SEXUAL FANTASIES 点缀其中，可由网络电商<a href=\"https://www.ssense.com/en-us/men/designers/vetements\" rel=\"nofollow\"> SSENSE </a>购买，定价 85-90 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101702NVQp0J5KCtdRwgnf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101702lYA75iWKBdjZGbFc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101702TufKVDH2MRBESr01.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612201017034fNY5FDEgdvZ10VM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612201017096zcfSRiBXAPvIgMq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>美国洛杉矶 Petersen Automotive Museum 展出已故艺术家 Keith Haring 的手绘汽车系列。Keith Haring 是 1980 年代美国著名的街头绘画艺术家和社会运动者。这次展出的汽车是 Keith 花了约 9 年时间所绘的 5 架车款。本次展览名为<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/keith-haring-petersen-automotive-museum-exhibition\" rel=\"nofollow\"> The Unconventional Canvases of Keith Haring</a>，展览时间将持续至明年的 6 月 4 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101724JDIl0oxHrXFZQgyR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101724jr97B3Rb1Y6COUud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101724pyfTwtLW1HvmNIo2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101725AtDeUIlbomLiEJ1N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101725eptk1SgFf20DZK5x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101726b7R6JkYvB4sLFpHA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101726w0JoBEcLyQNhuSex.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101728rc3jEsnpJ8QK4Cf0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612201017365h6je21SAwuJdsNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101736qOp621rv7FVB9Xbx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101736BtHijSLTg7Rkof4y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">摄影师<a href=\"http://www.creativeboom.com/inspiration/toys-photographer-documents-100-years-of-iconic-must-have-toys-and-games/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Kevin Fox </a>出了一本书，这本书记录了 100 年里出现的那些著名的玩具。这本书在亚马逊有售，售价为 30 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612201017595scdPX0EQYt7e3iz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631395\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101759w9aAvoPbzfD7HETn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101800NG7aVXgU9LxKptyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631395\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101800pRWzd0BkqZe1XsHI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631395\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101800F57wSWLaGVKIznZU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631395\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101800zevjQL7VfB2NZokd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637209\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/19/bape-transformers-optimus-prime-black-camo/#slide-3\" rel=\"nofollow\">BAPE 即将推出黑色迷彩版的变形金刚</a>，具体发售信息目前还未公布。不过，这款变形金刚明确只在日本市场销售，售价大概为 150 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612201018261FPTA7qQUynLozls.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101826y3SowFTgZrGEaQYH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161220101838vcGM3j541D7WA8Tf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/legoland-japan-coming-soon\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}